# Generated Geode runtime data
#
# Keep source, schemas, fixtures, docs, and curated control-plane files in Git.
# Keep bulk downloads and pipeline run output out of Git; for large live runs,
# prefer --root outside OneDrive or other sync-managed folders.
.geode_runtime/
_RAW_ARCHIVE/**
_SNAPSHOTS/**
